Health Point - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 

Health Point is an app designed specifically for people with visual empairment as an informational tool for medicines, their ingredients, and their side effects.
Additionally, the app contains an Apple Foundation Model as a chatbot, where users can interact with it to get information on the medicines they wish to know. It
contains a database that a Chatbot can access to for the user to get better information. Additionally, the Chatbot can be communicated using Voice to Text technology.

FOLDER CONTENTS - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
The code is divided into 3 main segments, ChatBotDir, Models, and Views.

The ChatBotDir contains most of the configuration for the chatbot itself, this includes it's personality prompts, how it contsults information from the database,
and how it manages the chats.

The Models folder contains most of the Backend of the code, focusing on transferring the information from databases into information that the users can access or
talk through with the chatbot.

Finally, the Views folder contains most of the code. Here is where most of the views are designed, and how most of the functionality as to how everything is displayed
and threaded together is. 

EXTERNAL IMPORTS - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
For the voice to text function, we used a TranscriptionKit, ThemeKit and TimerKit to make it work. To download these packages, head to:
https://developer.apple.com/tutorials/app-dev-training/transcribing-speech-to-text

APP USAGE - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
To use the app, simply make sure that the packages are included. Once these are ready, you can launch the app on any device that contains Apple Inteligence, and feel
free to use any function.

APP STATUS - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
Currently the app is ready for usage, but there is still room to add many new features and improvements.
